# Idearockers – Cursor Rules (Lightweight)

## Scope
Small Next.js 15 App Router site with Tailwind + shadcn/ui. No backend in this repo. i18n via `?hl=de` (default EN).

## Directories
- `app/` – routes, layouts, SEO metadata, sitemap/robots
- `components/` – UI, hero, sections
- `translations/` – `en/` and `de/` grouped JSON: `main.json`, `projects.json`, `impress.json`, `privacy.json`

## Non‑negotiables
- Keep `Footer` global in `app/layout.tsx`
- Dark theme default via `ThemeProvider` (class strategy)
- Titles: default slogan; per‑route titles in `app/impress/layout.tsx` and `app/privacy/layout.tsx`
- Sitemap/robots live at `app/sitemap.ts` and `app/robots.ts`

## Language switching
- Query param `hl=de` toggles German; links must preserve `hl`
- No `/de` path prefix

## Commit style
- Conventional commits only (feat/fix/chore/refactor/docs)
- Work on `develop`; PRs from feature branches → `develop`; later merge to `main`

## Don’ts
- Don’t add server rendering of theme class; we accept client application with hydration warning suppressed
- Don’t introduce new data sources or analytics without updating privacy policy and consent

